    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被宇宙海盗追杀的史莱狗，被迫降落到一个神秘的星球上。为了能够离开这个星球，史莱狗开始了在这个星球上的冒险</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/6617974dcd82eeb1ed24c97c31369c45.poster.avif?t=1760668427\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/6617974dcd82eeb1ed24c97c31369c45.webm?t=1760668427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >sr400星球总共有四个风格完全不同的区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >sdog村：sdog村里的生物酷爱南瓜，村中还有一个神秘的能力能够让其他生物自由的变大缩小。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/48a6faa02ec1eb5d40c3a9025f036f33.gif?t=1760668427\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/48a6faa02ec1eb5d40c3a9025f036f33.poster.avif?t=1760668427\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雨林：雨林的深处有数座神庙，曾经有个神秘的女战士开着飞船降落在那里，这会不会是离开这个星球的关键？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/1374532f619f0adc92c9d4e086c76479.poster.avif?t=1760668427\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/1374532f619f0adc92c9d4e086c76479.webm?t=1760668427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >火上：沉寂了许久的火山又开始喷发，不断掉下的巨石让生活在那里的生物苦不堪言。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/345c77aad10ed313dfd395d0d49da8ca.poster.avif?t=1760668427\" width=650 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/345c77aad10ed313dfd395d0d49da8ca.webm?t=1760668427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/345c77aad10ed313dfd395d0d49da8ca.mp4?t=1760668427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冰原：冰原的统治者似乎控制着整个星球，一切的灾难似乎都因它而起。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/a471010a1214d8bb16d08116da694f1e.poster.avif?t=1760668427\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/a471010a1214d8bb16d08116da694f1e.webm?t=1760668427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解密</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个区域都有符合其风格的解密元素，解开谜题，能够获得让角色变得更强力的道具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请帮助史莱狗离开这个星球，在各个区域尽情的探索吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
